DNS in Linux

ping db from App host

cat >/etc/hosts

192.168.1.11 db
192.168.1.11 www.google.com

we can use any name to reach the system db
ping, ssh

curl 

for small setup, we can configure DNS


DNS server, All the hosts will map to DNS server

/etc/resolve.conf

nameserver 192.168.1.100

ping db


